          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1679396972845-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 3-4 min turn the <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> and add the <strong>sticky sauce </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until the basa is cooked through and the sauce has thickened to a sticky consistency – this is your <strong>sticky Chinese-style basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1679396976484-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
